quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,170,"Si …ďe wi'amaa:"Jokkee kon ko Allah Jippini", …ďe mbi'a:"Ko woni, men njokkay ko men tawri kon baabiraa…ďe amen"; si tawii noon baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen hakkilataa hay e huunde …ďe peewataa?!"
  2,171,"Yeru …ďen yeddu…ďe hono ono ewnotoo…óo kon ko nanataa si wanaa noddaandu e ewnal. Ko fah…óu…ďe, mum…óu…ďe, wum…ďe …ďe kakkiltaa."
  2,172,"Heey mon gom…óim…ďe! √Ďamee immorde he laa…ďu…ói …ói men Arsiki on, jaarnon Allah si on wonii ko kanko rewoton."
  2,173,"Anndee ko o Harminani on, ko jiibe (jiiba), e ∆īii∆īam, e teewu kose, e [huunde hirsiraande] daginiraande ko woori Allah. Kala on du√Īaa…óo [e √Īaamugol …óum] hara wanaa …ďew…óo wanaa jaggitu…óo, bakkaatu fawaaki mo. Pellet Allah ko ya'fotoo…óo Yurmotoo…óo."
  2,174,"Pellet …ďen suu…óoo…ďe ko Allah Jippini kon e deftere nden, hi…ďe soodira …óum cogguwel fam…óungel. ∆Āen …óon alaa wa…óude ka deedi ma…ď…ďe si wanaa yiite ngen; Allah haaldataa he ma…ď…ďe √Īalnde darngal, o La…ď…ďiŇčtaa …ďe, hino woodani …ďe lepte muusu…óe."
  2,175,"Ko …ďen ngoni soodir…ďe majjere peewal, e lepte ya'fuya. kaawse ko mu√Ī√Īori…ďe ka yiite!"
  2,176,"∆äuum noon, ko fii Allah Jippinirii deftere ndee goonga. pellet …ďeen luutondir…ďe e deftere ndee ,e…ďe he luural wo…ó…óungal."